name: Noir Cat (E. Lisle)
description:
Noir cat is a inspiration from 60´ambient place. I am an illustrator, fond of painting. My works have not been published on any NFT site. Hen is the first site where I publish NFT.

This illustration was based on the spirit of the small Argentine towns in the 60´.
When a golden haze covered the nostalgia. When life was so simple than music on an old instrument.
And a cat on the wall with its simplicity were enough to consider us rich.
This is how my grandparents thought, this is how I hope I have captured that spirit in this work.
